<title>USA: Elron to invest $2.5 mln in software co.</title>
<headline>Elron to invest $2.5 mln in software co.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-08-06</dateline>
<text>
<p>Elron Electronic Industries Ltd said Wednesday that it has an agreement to invest $2.5 million for 15.8 percent of the share capital of EliaShim Ltd, and was granted an option, for 18 months, to invest additional $4 million and increase its holding up to 27 percent.</p>
<p>EliaShim specializes in information security, anti-virus and anti-vandal software.</p>
